outdoor sports headquarters inc in willowbrook at first i 
thought it was funny you know hey the phones dont work now i 
guess its pretty serious 
i still run my regular route to stores that want hunting and 
fishing stuff but i really cant tell what they might need if i 
dont have a phone tweed said heck i cant even call my boss 
in dayton ohio 
he said he spends much of his time reading magazines and talking 
to two secretaries 
how are we coping this is how were coping says vicki 
riendeau chewing a candy bar with her legs up on the desk if 
this keeps up ill be a raving lunatic weve looked at the files 
and already rearranged what we rearranged last week what else is 
there 
among the hardest hit are 24000 florists nationwide that belong 
to ftd inc the flower delivery network 
about half are hooked to a computer system in downers grove 
designed to relay an order across the country in a snap but the 
line to the ftd computer network flows through the hinsdale station 
weve been absolutely crippled said bob poirier director 
of operations for ftd subsidiary floral network inc who has the 
task of trying to find an alternative system 
the flower business has not stopped people can still call 
and order but instead of using the computer network florists have 
to look up florists in other cities and call them one by one that 
hurts 
the switching station meanwhile has come to resemble a 
traveling circus 
big mess tents are erected for the dozens of laborers assigned 
to get the site back in order and illinois bell executives call 
the shots from a row of trailers customers line up at a bank of 
portable pay phones trucked in by the utility 
its been a disaster but its folksy said nancy ging a 
