school in camden del fashioned a bass fiddle from a potato chip 
can broomstick handle and venetian blind cord for a competition 
called the sound of music all contestants were required to play 
america the beautiful on instruments from nonmusical objects 
at the end they formed their own orchestra 
in addition to winners in the individual events the school with 
the highest point total captured the division haverford pa high 
school won the senior division while campus junior high school in 
irmo sc captured the junior division title 
