shutdown about the same level it had reached on may 19 when a 
water gauge problem caused the reactor to automatically power down 
it was a relatively minor instrumentation problem that we can 
correct said janice brady a plant spokeswoman as weve said 
repeatedly because of the complexity of any nuclear plant its 
not uncommon for a unit to automatically shut down 
