<TEXT>
by almost any definition the annual inflation 
rate is under 5 percent and unlikely to move much higher than that 
in the near future 
but as you probably have suspected that doesnt mean your 
personal rate cant rise faster than that if you are inclined 
toward socalled finer things your inflation rate could be close 
