immediate 25cent wage increase that is to be deducted from future 
costofliving increases in increments of 10 cents 10 cents and 5 
cents 
the 6500 urw members who work for uniroyal goodrich tire co 
ratified a threeyear agreement by may 16 that guarantees against 
plant closings but includes a limitation on costofliving raises 
during the first year the union said 
the urw demonstrated its concern for keeping uniroyal goodrich 
viable and we trust this will pay off in future improvements for 
these members stone said 
